Press, 45&ndash;64; reprinted in Woolhouse (ed.) 1994, 82&ndash;104.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 1993, <em>Descartes, Spinoza, Leibniz: the
concept of substance in seventeenth century metaphysics</em>, London
and New York: Routledge.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash; (ed.), 1994. <em>Gottfried Wilhelm Leibniz:
Critical Assessments</em> (Volume 2), London and New York:
Routledge.</li>

<li>Zycinski, J., 1989. &ldquo;The Doctrine of Substance and
Whitehead&rsquo;s Metaphysics&rdquo;, <em>The Review of
Metaphysics</em>, 2(4): 765&ndash;781.</li>
</ul>
